HID (from picture):
[usb] pm3 --> lf hid wiegand
This command converts facility code/card number to Wiegand code          
          
Usage: lf hid wiegand [h] [OEM] [FC] [CN]          
Options:          
       h             - This help          
       OEM           - OEM number / site code          
       FC            - facility code          
       CN            - card number          
Examples:          
      lf hid wiegand 0 101 2001
